{"title":"Lapsed","description":"","products":[{"product_id":"bee-it-shampoo-body-wash-blue-for-kids-250ml","title":"BEE IT Shampoo \u0026 Body Wash Blue for Kids 250ml","description":"\u003cp class=\"MsoNormal\"\u003ePhysiological pH shampoo \u0026amp; body wash rich in natural ingredients to enjoy the bath time as a pleasant experience of play and creativity. With organic aloe vera, sweet almond oil, organic honey and propolis, for a delicate and nourishing action.\u003cbr\u003eAmused and clean, his hair will be velvety and luminous, and his skin will be even softer and more fragrant.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"MsoNormal\"\u003e\u003cb\u003eHow to use:\u003c\/b\u003e Apply to hair and body and massage gently, then rinse.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"MsoNormal\"\u003e\u003cb\u003eIngredients:\u003c\/b\u003e Aqua, Magnesium lauryl sulfate, Cocamidopropyl betaine, Coco-glucoside, Glyceryl oleate, Guar hydroxypropyltrimonium chloride, Glycerin, Aloe barbadensis leaf juice*, Parfum, Sodium benzoate, Potassium sorbate, Sodium chloride, Benzyl alcohol, Myristyl lactate, Prunus amygdalus dulcis oil, Helianthus annuus seed oil, Citric acid, Calendula officinalis extract, Dehydroacetic acid, Mel*, Propolis, Tocopherol.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"MsoNormal\"\u003e*Organic\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"MsoNormal\"\u003eNatural product with physiological pH 4.5-5.5\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"MsoNormal\"\u003eAnimal Friendly | No Paraffin | No Silicones | No Parabens | 100% Recyclable\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"MsoNormal\"\u003e“Less plastic is fantastic” packaging is using 70% less plastic compared to a normal bottle pack. Less bulk, being soft and doesn’t break, generates a better recycling chain and allows use of all its contents.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"MsoNormal\"\u003eBy purchasing BEE IT cosmetics  you contribute to the creation of new bee oasis. \u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"MsoNormal\"\u003eMade in Italy\u003c\/p\u003e","brand":"BEE IT","offers":[{"title":"Default Title","offer_id":49354588979527,"sku":null,"price":12.0,"currency_code":"EUR","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0790\/6829\/9591\/files\/bee-it-shampoo-body-wash-blue-for-kids-250ml-687213.png?v=1739897342"},{"product_id":"bee-it-shampoo-body-wash-pink-for-kids-250ml","title":"BEE IT Shampoo \u0026 Body Wash Pink for Kids 250ml","description":"\u003cp class=\"MsoNormal\"\u003ePhysiological pH shampoo \u0026amp; body wash rich in natural ingredients to enjoy the bath time as a pleasant experience of play and creativity. With organic aloe vera, sweet almond oil, organic honey and propolis, for a delicate and nourishing action.\u003cbr\u003eAmused and clean, his hair will be velvety and luminous, and his skin will be even softer and more fragrant.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"MsoNormal\"\u003e\u003cb\u003eHow to use:\u003c\/b\u003e Apply to hair and body and massage gently, then rinse.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"MsoNormal\"\u003e\u003cb\u003eIngredients:\u003c\/b\u003e Aqua, Magnesium lauryl sulfate, Cocamidopropyl betaine, Coco-glucoside, Glyceryl oleate, Guar hydroxypropyltrimonium chloride, Glycerin, Aloe barbadensis leaf juice*, Parfum, Sodium benzoate, Potassium sorbate, Sodium chloride, Benzyl alcohol, Myristyl lactate, Prunus amygdalus dulcis oil, Helianthus annuus seed oil, Citric acid, Calendula officinalis extract, Dehydroacetic acid, Mel*, Propolis, Tocopherol.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"MsoNormal\"\u003e*Organic\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"MsoNormal\"\u003eNatural product with physiological pH 4.5-5.5\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"MsoNormal\"\u003eAnimal Friendly | No Paraffin | No Silicones | No Parabens | 100% Recyclable\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"MsoNormal\"\u003e“Less plastic is fantastic” packaging is using 70% less plastic compared to a normal bottle pack. Less bulk, being soft and doesn’t break, generates a better recycling chain and allows use of all its contents.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"MsoNormal\"\u003eBy purchasing BEE IT cosmetics  you contribute to the creation of new bee oasis. \u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"MsoNormal\"\u003eMade in Italy\u003c\/p\u003e","brand":"BEE IT","offers":[{"title":"Default Title","offer_id":49354641178951,"sku":null,"price":12.0,"currency_code":"EUR","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0790\/6829\/9591\/files\/bee-it-shampoo-body-wash-pink-for-kids-250ml-813819.png?v=1739897342"},{"product_id":"naif-mineral-sunscreen-spray-spf50-for-baby-kids-100ml","title":"NAIF Mineral Sunscreen Spray SPF50 for Baby \u0026 Kids 100ml","description":"\u003cp\u003eNaif Mineral Sunscreen Spray SPF50 is developed for the sensitive skin of a baby and kids with a reef-friendly formula. \u003cspan\u003eThe zinc-oxide based mineral filter protects the skin immediately against UVA and UVB with minimum risk of skin irritation. The convenient spray makes for a quick and easy application. Immediate effectiveness against UVA and UVB radiation.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eHow to use: \u003c\/strong\u003e\u003cspan\u003eShake the spray before use. Apply a generous amount to the body and face before your kids go in the sun. Reapply every two hours and after swimming for optimum protection. Do not keep product in the sun.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eIngredients:\u003c\/strong\u003e \u003cspan\u003eDecyl Oleate, Zinc Oxide, Coco-Caprylate\/Caprate, Alcohol, Triheptanoin, Polyhydroxystearic Acid, Allantoin, Tocopherol, Aqua\/Water, Silica Dimethyl Silylate, Pongamol, Helianthus Annuus Seed Oil, Bisabolol, Denatonium Benzoate.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eBottle made from bioplastic\u003c\/p\u003e","brand":"NAIF","offers":[{"title":"Default Title","offer_id":49445499142471,"sku":"","price":23.9,"currency_code":"EUR","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0790\/6829\/9591\/files\/naif-mineral-sunscreen-spray-spf50-for-baby-kids-100ml-887359.png?v=1739897345"},{"product_id":"naif-mineral-sunscreen-spf50-for-baby-kids-100ml","title":"NAIF Mineral Sunscreen SPF50 for Baby \u0026 Kids 100ml","description":"\u003cp\u003eNaif Mineral Sunscreen Spray SPF50 is developed for the sensitive skin of a baby and kids with a reef-friendly formula. \u003cspan\u003eThe zinc oxide based UV filter protects the skin immediately with minimum risk of skin irritation.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eThe zinc oxide based UV filter adds a protective layer on top of the skin which reflects the sunbeams. This results in immediate effectiveness against UVA and UVB radiation. The added natural oils make application easy and hydrates the skin.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eHow to use: \u003c\/strong\u003e\u003cspan\u003eShake the sunscreen before use. Apply a generous amount evenly to the body and face before your kids go in the sun. Reapply every two hours and after swimming for optimum protection. Do not keep product in the sun.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eIngredients:\u003c\/strong\u003e \u003cspan\u003eDecyl Oleate, Zinc Oxide, Caprylic\/Capric Triglyceride, Triheptanoin, Coco-Caprylate\/Caprate, Hydrogenated Vegetable Oil, Dextrin Palmitate, Parfum\/Fragrance, Tocopherol, Polyhydroxystearic Acid, Allantoin, Helianthus Annuus Seed Oil, Bisabolol, Pongamol, Palmitic Acid.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eTube made from recycled plastic\u003c\/p\u003e","brand":"NAIF","offers":[{"title":"Default Title","offer_id":49445547737415,"sku":null,"price":22.9,"currency_code":"EUR","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0790\/6829\/9591\/files\/naif-mineral-sunscreen-spf50-for-baby-kids-100ml-103208.png?v=1739897347"},{"product_id":"naif-plastic-free-wipes-54pcs","title":"NAIF Plastic Free Wipes 54pcs","description":"\u003cp\u003eNaif baby wipes clean and protect the baby's bum, body and face. The lotion is made from 99% water and does not contain perfume and alcohol. Suitable for sensitive and dry skin. Naif wipes are plastic free and are prepared from wood-based fibers sourced from sustainably managed forests.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eHow to use: \u003c\/strong\u003eWhile changing, open the package with one hand, holding your baby with the other. Wipe the area well and don't forget the folds. When finished, close the package tightly to prevent dehydration.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eIngredients:\u003c\/strong\u003e \u003cspan\u003eAqua\/Water, Sodium Cocoyl Glutamate, Levulinic Acid, Sodium Benzoate, Citric Acid\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e","brand":"NAIF","offers":[{"title":"Default Title","offer_id":49445910675783,"sku":null,"price":3.95,"currency_code":"EUR","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0790\/6829\/9591\/files\/naif-plastic-free-wipes-54pcs-717208.png?v=1739897339"},{"product_id":"naif-2-in-1-shampoo-conditioner-for-kids-200ml","title":"NAIF 2-in-1 Shampoo \u0026 Conditioner for Kids 200ml","description":"\u003cp\u003e2-in-1 kids Shampoo \u0026amp; Conditioner for all hairtypes (long, short, thick or curly). The shampoo cleanses your hair while the anti-tangle formula ensures that the hair is soft and easy to comb through. Softens and detangles hair and hydrates with sunflower- and linseed oil. For all kids. Without SLES or microplastics.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eMild, fruity scent developed for and by children.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eHow to use: \u003c\/strong\u003eTake a coin-sized amount of Naif 2-in-1 Shampoo and Conditioner and massage into wet hair. Leave it in for a bit, rinse.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eIngredients:\u003c\/strong\u003e Aqua\/Water, Coco-Glucoside, Sodium Coco-Sulfate, Cocamidopropyl Betaine, Glycerin, Hydrolyzed Wheat Protein, Gossypium Hirsutum (Cotton) Seed Extract, Panthenol, Pantolactone, Betaine, Inulin, Guar Hydroxypropyltrimonium Chloride, Glyceryl Oleate, Tocopherol, Hydrogenated Palm Glycerides Citrate, Sodium Levulinate, Sodium Anisate, Sodium Chloride, Fragrance, Citric Acid, Sodium Hydroxide\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eTube made from bioplastic\u003c\/p\u003e","brand":"NAIF","offers":[{"title":"Default Title","offer_id":49445993644359,"sku":null,"price":11.9,"currency_code":"EUR","in_stock":false}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0790\/6829\/9591\/files\/naif-2-in-1-shampoo-conditioner-for-kids-200ml-851648.png?v=1739897337"},{"product_id":"naif-nourishing-shampoo-for-kids-200ml","title":"NAIF Nourishing Shampoo for Kids 200ml","description":"\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eA nourishing shampoo developed specifically to tame those wild kids' hairs. The shampoo cleanses and softens the hair to make it easier to comb through. \u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003eNaif's kids shampoo contains a special anti-tangle formula and is packed with a selection of natural ingredients, like cottonseed extract and hydrolyzed wheat protein. Cares for both hair and scalp, without microplastics, silicones and SLES. So, it’s mild for the eyes too.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eHow to use: \u003c\/strong\u003eApply a coin-sized amount of shampoo and massage into wet hair, rinse.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eIngredients:\u003c\/strong\u003e \u003cspan\u003eAqua\/Water, Coco-Glucoside, Sodium Coco-Sulfate, Cocamidopropyl Betaine, Glycerin, Hydrolyzed Wheat Protein, Gossypium Hirsutum (Cotton) Seed Extract, Panthenol, Pantolactone, Betaine, Guar Hydroxypropyltrimonium Chloride, Glyceryl Oleate, Tocopherol, Hydrogenated Palm Glycerides Citrate, Sodium Levulinate, Sodium Anisate, Sodium Chloride, Parfum\/Fragrance, Citric Acid, Sodium Hydroxide\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eTube made from bioplastic\u003c\/p\u003e","brand":"NAIF","offers":[{"title":"Default Title","offer_id":49446040371527,"sku":null,"price":11.9,"currency_code":"EUR","in_stock":false}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0790\/6829\/9591\/files\/naif-nourishing-shampoo-for-kids-200ml-208574.png?v=1739897339"},{"product_id":"naif-softening-conditioner-for-kids-200ml","title":"NAIF Softening Conditioner for Kids 200ml","description":"\u003cp\u003eCurly hair, coarse hair, thick hair - Naïf's Kids Conditioner nourishes and softens the hair of our little ones and makes it easy to comb through. Thanks to the addition of cottonseed oil, the hair is not only cared for, but also frizz-free. Suitable for all hair types.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"MsoNormal\"\u003e\u003cspan style=\"mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;\"\u003eRemoves tangles and moisturizes the hair with sunflower and linseed oil. No SLES and microplastics. \u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"MsoNormal\"\u003e\u003cspan style=\"mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;\"\u003eMild and fruity fragrance - developed by and for kids.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"MsoNormal\"\u003e\u003cb\u003e\u003cspan style=\"mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;\"\u003eHow to use: \u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/b\u003e\u003cspan style=\"mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;\"\u003eUse the conditioner after shampoo and apply from the ends only. Let it sit and rinse! You can use the conditioner after every wash.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"MsoNormal\"\u003e\u003cb\u003e\u003cspan style=\"mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;\"\u003eIngredients:\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/b\u003e\u003cspan style=\"mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;\"\u003e Aqua\/Water, Cetearyl Alcohol, Glycerin, Glyceryl Stearate SE, Distearoylethyl Hydroxyethylmonium Methosulfate, Stearamidopropyl Dimethylamine, Gossypium Herbaceum (Cotton) Seed Oil, Panthenol, Pantolactone, Tocopherol, Helianthus Annuus Seed Oil, Hydroxyethylcellulose, Behentrimonium Chloride, Dipropylene Glycol, Sodium Levulinate, Sodium Anisate, Fragrance, Citric Acid, Sodium Hydroxide\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"MsoNormal\"\u003e\u003cspan style=\"mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;\"\u003eTube made from bioplastic\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e","brand":"NAIF","offers":[{"title":"Default Title","offer_id":49446052004167,"sku":null,"price":11.9,"currency_code":"EUR","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0790\/6829\/9591\/files\/naif-softening-conditioner-for-kids-200ml-924525.png?v=1739897345"},{"product_id":"naif-easy-styling-hair-lotion-for-baby-kids-150ml","title":"NAIF Easy Styling Hair Lotion for Baby \u0026 Kids 150ml","description":"\u003cp class=\"MsoNormal\"\u003e\u003cspan style=\"mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;\"\u003eA hair lotion to tame and take care of wild kids hair. Naïf's Easy Styling Hair Lotion makes combing easier and reduces tangles and frizz for all hair types. \u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli style=\"mso-list: l0 level1 lfo1; tab-stops: list 36.0pt;\" class=\"MsoNormal\"\u003e\u003cspan style=\"mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;\"\u003eHair lotion with natural ingredients that doesn't make the hair greasy\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli style=\"mso-list: l0 level1 lfo1; tab-stops: list 36.0pt;\" class=\"MsoNormal\"\u003e\u003cspan style=\"mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;\"\u003eSoftens knots and tangles in the hair and reduces frizz in curls\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli style=\"mso-list: l0 level1 lfo1; tab-stops: list 36.0pt;\" class=\"MsoNormal\"\u003e\u003cspan style=\"mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;\"\u003eCan also be used with cradle cap\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"mso-list: l0 level1 lfo1; tab-stops: list 36.0pt;\"\u003e\u003cspan style=\"mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;\"\u003eFor use on babies and children, for all hairtypes\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"mso-list: l0 level1 lfo1; tab-stops: list 36.0pt;\"\u003e\u003cspan style=\"mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;\"\u003eDoes not contain microplastics, mineral oils, SLES or silicones\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003c\/ul\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"MsoNormal\"\u003e\u003cb\u003e\u003cspan style=\"mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;\"\u003eHow to use: \u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/b\u003e\u003cspan style=\"mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;\"\u003eSpray on towel-dried hair from 30 cm away. Massage gently, comb through the hair and style. Suitable for daily use.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"MsoNormal\"\u003e\u003cb\u003e\u003cspan style=\"mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;\"\u003eIngredients:\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/b\u003e\u003cspan style=\"mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;\"\u003e Aqua\/Water, Methylpropanediol, Caprylyl\/Capryl Glucoside, Glycerin, Gossypium Hirsutum (Cotton Seed) Extract, Caprylyl Glycol, Phenylpropanol, Inulin, Betaine, Sodium Cocoyl Glutamate, Glyceryl Caprylate, Polyglyceryl-6 Oleate, Sodium Surfactin, Parfum\/Fragrance (allergen-free), Lactic Acid, Citric Acid, Sodium Hydroxide\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"MsoNormal\"\u003e\u003cspan style=\"mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;\"\u003eBottle made from recycled plastic\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e","brand":"NAIF","offers":[{"title":"Default Title","offer_id":49446066323783,"sku":null,"price":14.9,"currency_code":"EUR","in_stock":false}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0790\/6829\/9591\/files\/naif-easy-styling-hair-lotion-for-baby-kids-150ml-404694.png?v=1739897336"},{"product_id":"naif-relaxing-bath-foam-for-baby-kids-500ml","title":"NAIF Relaxing Bath Foam for Baby \u0026 Kids 200ml","description":"\u003cp class=\"MsoNormal\"\u003e\u003cspan style=\"mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;\"\u003eWorry-free fun in the bath with lots of bubbles made with natural ingredients. Naif Relaxing Bath Foam for Baby \u0026amp; Kids nurtures, cleanses mildly, hydrates and promises plenty of fun.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli class=\"MsoNormal\"\u003e\u003cspan style=\"mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;\"\u003eBath foam with natural derivatives from coconut oil\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli class=\"MsoNormal\"\u003e\u003cspan style=\"mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;\"\u003eCleanses and hydrates the skin while bathing\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli class=\"MsoNormal\"\u003e\u003cspan style=\"mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;\"\u003eDoes not contain microplastics, mineral oils, SLES\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003c\/ul\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan style=\"mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;\"\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eHow to use: \u003c\/strong\u003eFill the bath and add a dash of bath foam to the bath water. Mix until you see the first bubbles appear.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"MsoNormal\"\u003e\u003cb\u003e\u003cspan style=\"mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;\"\u003eIngredients:\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/b\u003e\u003cspan style=\"mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;\"\u003e Aqua, Sodium Coco-Sulfate, Coco-Glucoside, Glycerin, Cocamidopropyl Betaine, Parfum, Hydrolyzed Wheat Protein, Gossypium Herbaceum Seed Extract, Glyceryl Oleat, Tocopherol, Hydrogenated Palm Glycerides Citrate, Sodium Levulinate, Sodium Anisate, Sodium Chloride, Glycol Distearate, Citric Acid, Sodium Hydroxide\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"MsoNormal\"\u003e\u003cspan style=\"mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;\"\u003eTube\/bottle made from recycled plastic\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e","brand":"NAIF","offers":[{"title":"Default Title","offer_id":49446184714567,"sku":"","price":6.9,"currency_code":"EUR","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0790\/6829\/9591\/files\/naif-relaxing-bath-foam-for-baby-kids-200ml-869986.png?v=1739897344"},{"product_id":"naif-cleansing-wash-gel-200ml","title":"NAIF Cleansing Wash Gel 200ml","description":"\u003cp\u003eNaïf cleansing wash gel for baby \u0026amp; kids cleanses the skin mildly and prevents dry skin.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"mso-list: l0 level1 lfo1; tab-stops: list 36.0pt;\"\u003e\u003cspan style=\"mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;\"\u003eWashing gel for bath and shower\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"mso-list: l0 level1 lfo1; tab-stops: list 36.0pt;\"\u003e\u003cspan style=\"mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;\"\u003eCleanses and cares for the sensitive baby skin with natural oils\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli style=\"mso-list: l0 level1 lfo1; tab-stops: list 36.0pt;\" class=\"MsoNormal\"\u003e\u003cspan style=\"mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;\"\u003e0% SLES\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli style=\"mso-list: l0 level1 lfo1; tab-stops: list 36.0pt;\" class=\"MsoNormal\"\u003e\u003cspan style=\"mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;\"\u003eWithout microplastics and mineral oils\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003c\/ul\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan style=\"mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;\"\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eHow to use:\u003c\/strong\u003e Apply a small amount to the baby's skin. Rinse off and dry. \u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"MsoNormal\"\u003e\u003cb\u003e\u003cspan style=\"mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;\"\u003eIngredients:\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/b\u003e\u003cspan style=\"mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;\"\u003e Aqua\/Water, Coco-Glucoside (\u003ci\u003ecloudy liquid derived from coconut\u003c\/i\u003e), Sodium Coco-Sulfate (\u003ci\u003emade from the fatty acids of coconut oil\u003c\/i\u003e), Cocamidopropyl Betaine (\u003ci\u003enaturally-derived surfactant that is sourced from coconut oil\u003c\/i\u003e), Glycerin, Hydrolyzed Wheat Protein, Gossypium Hirsutum (Cotton Seed) Extract, Glyceryl Oleate, Tocopherol, Hydrogenated Palm Glycerides Citrate, Sodium Levulinate, Sodium Anisate, Sodium Chloride, Fragrance (allergen-free), Citric Acid, Sodium Hydroxide\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"MsoNormal\"\u003e\u003cspan style=\"mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;\"\u003eTube made from recycled plastic\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e","brand":"NAIF","offers":[{"title":"Default Title","offer_id":49446208602439,"sku":null,"price":10.9,"currency_code":"EUR","in_stock":false}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0790\/6829\/9591\/files\/naif-cleansing-wash-gel-200ml-254915.png?v=1739897263"},{"product_id":"naif-cleansing-wash-gel-200ml-copy","title":"NAIF Zinc Diaper Cream 75ml","description":"\u003cdiv class=\"css-ss00rg\" data-slate-node=\"element\"\u003e\n\u003cspan\u003eA zinc cream for Baby \u0026amp; Kids. Helps with and prevents diaper rash. No perfume added and suitable for damaged skin. \u003c\/span\u003eZinc dehydrates the skin, which is exactly what is needed to prevent or take care of diaper rash. Diapers prevent the air from circulating, resulting in wet and soft skin. This combined with pee and poo makes the skin extra sensitive to irritation and rashes.\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003cdiv class=\"css-ss00rg\" data-slate-node=\"element\"\u003e\n\u003cul data-mce-fragment=\"1\"\u003e\n\u003cli style=\"font-weight: 400;\" data-mce-fragment=\"1\"\u003e\u003cspan style=\"font-weight: 400;\" data-mce-fragment=\"1\"\u003eBaby diaper cream with natural ingredients like zinc oxide, camomile and vitamin E\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli style=\"font-weight: 400;\" data-mce-fragment=\"1\"\u003e\u003cspan style=\"font-weight: 400;\" data-mce-fragment=\"1\"\u003eSoothes and repairs skin irritations and diaper rash\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli style=\"font-weight: 400;\" data-mce-fragment=\"1\"\u003e\u003cspan style=\"font-weight: 400;\" data-mce-fragment=\"1\"\u003eUse also for diaper rash prevention, after every diaper change\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003c\/ul\u003e\n\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eHow to use: \u003c\/strong\u003eOpen the tube with one hand. Apply a small amount to the dry and clean baby bum. Spread lightly. \u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eIngredients: \u003c\/strong\u003eAqua\/Water, Zinc Oxide, Caprylic\/Capric Triglyceride, Sorbitan Olivate, Polyglyceryl-2 Dipolyhydroxystearate, Glycerin, Magnesium Sulfate, Phenethyl Alcohol, Prunus Amygdalus Dulcis (Sweet Almond) Oil, Persea Gratissima (Avocado) Oil, Macadamia Integrifolia Seed Oil, Gossypium Herbaceum (Cotton) Seed Oil, Tocopherol, Helianthus Annuus (Sunflower) Seed Oil, Bisabolol, Hydrogenated Castor Oil, Caprylyl Glycol, Propanediol, Lactic Acid, Sodium Hydroxide\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eTube made from recycled plastic\u003c\/p\u003e","brand":"NAIF","offers":[{"title":"Default Title","offer_id":49446219022663,"sku":null,"price":12.5,"currency_code":"EUR","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0790\/6829\/9591\/files\/naif-zinc-diaper-cream-75ml-526868.png?v=1739897265"},{"product_id":"naif-nurturing-baby-cream-75ml","title":"NAIF Nurturing Baby Cream 75ml","description":"\u003cdiv class=\"css-ss00rg\" data-slate-node=\"element\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003eNurturing Cream is a hydrating cream for Baby \u0026amp; Kids. The cream nourishes dry and sensitive skin. With the help of sweet almond oil, avocado oil and macadamia oil the nurturing cream takes care of dry and sensitive skin and gives it some extra love. Suitable for body and face.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003cdiv class=\"css-ss00rg\" data-slate-node=\"element\"\u003e\n\u003cul data-mce-fragment=\"1\"\u003e\n\u003cli class=\"css-1eg5fk0\" data-slate-node=\"element\"\u003e\n\u003cdiv class=\"css-ss00rg\" data-slate-node=\"element\"\u003e\u003cspan data-slate-node=\"text\"\u003eMade with the best natural ingredients like sweet almond oil\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli class=\"css-1eg5fk0\" data-slate-node=\"element\"\u003e\n\u003cdiv class=\"css-ss00rg\" data-slate-node=\"element\"\u003e\u003cspan data-slate-node=\"text\"\u003eFor use on face and body\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli class=\"css-1eg5fk0\" data-slate-node=\"element\"\u003e\n\u003cdiv class=\"css-ss00rg\" data-slate-node=\"element\"\u003e\u003cspan data-slate-node=\"text\"\u003eNo microplastics and mineral oils\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli class=\"css-1eg5fk0\" data-slate-node=\"element\"\u003e\n\u003cdiv class=\"css-ss00rg\" data-slate-node=\"element\"\u003e\u003cspan data-slate-node=\"text\"\u003eDermatologically tested\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003c\/ul\u003e\n\u003cbr\u003e\n\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eHow to use: \u003c\/strong\u003eApply a small amount of nurturing cream, suitable for both face and body.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eIngredients: \u003c\/strong\u003eAqua\/Water, Prunus Amygdalus Dulcis (Sweet Almond) Oil, Macadamia Integrifolia Seed Oil, Persea Gratissima (Avocado) Oil, Glycerin, Gossypium Herbaceum (Cotton) Seed Oil, Cetyl Alcohol, Cetearyl Alcohol, Sucrose Stearate, Glyceryl Stearate Citrate, Phenethyl Alcohol, Helianthus Annuus (Sunflower) Seed Oil, Bisabolol, Xanthan Gum, Tocopherol, Caprylyl Glycol, Propanediol, Citric Acid, Sodium Hydroxide\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eTube made from recycled plastic\u003c\/p\u003e","brand":"NAIF","offers":[{"title":"Default Title","offer_id":49446277808455,"sku":null,"price":13.9,"currency_code":"EUR","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0790\/6829\/9591\/files\/naif-nurturing-baby-cream-75ml-913283.png?v=1739897268"},{"product_id":"naif-baby-balm-75ml-1","title":"NAIF Baby Balm 75ml","description":"\u003cp\u003eA multi-purpose balm to give dry skin some extra love. This balm with natural ingredients supports and protects the skin barrier. \u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"MsoNormal\"\u003e\u003cspan style=\"mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;\"\u003eNaïf Baby Balm 0% Perfume is a multi-purpose balm that forms a protective layer on dry (baby) skin which helps keep the moisture in. The balm softens skin and keeps it supple without completely closing off. Use it for dry cheeks or hands, chapped lips, sore nipples post-breastfeeding. \u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli style=\"mso-list: l0 level1 lfo1; tab-stops: list 36.0pt;\" class=\"MsoNormal\"\u003e\u003cspan style=\"mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;\"\u003eBalm with natural ingredients for extra dry baby skin\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli style=\"mso-list: l0 level1 lfo1; tab-stops: list 36.0pt;\" class=\"MsoNormal\"\u003e\u003cspan style=\"mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;\"\u003eSoothes and restores the very youngest skin and supports the skin barrier\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"mso-list: l0 level1 lfo1; tab-stops: list 36.0pt;\"\u003e\u003cspan style=\"mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;\"\u003eNo animal fats, microplastics and mineral oils\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"mso-list: l0 level1 lfo1; tab-stops: list 36.0pt;\"\u003e\u003cspan style=\"mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;\"\u003e0% perfume\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003c\/ul\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"MsoNormal\"\u003e\u003cb\u003e\u003cspan style=\"mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;\"\u003eHow to use: \u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/b\u003e\u003cspan style=\"mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;\"\u003eApply a small amount of salve, suitable for both face and body.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"MsoNormal\"\u003e\u003cb\u003e\u003cspan style=\"mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;\"\u003eIngredients: \u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/b\u003e\u003cspan style=\"mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;\"\u003eButyrospermum Parkii (Shea) Butter, Helianthus Annuus (Sunflower) Seed Oil, Sorbitan Olivate, Tribehenin, Simmondsia Chinensis (Jojoba) Seed Oil, Macadamia Integrifolia Seed Oil, Calendula Officinalis Flower Extract, Carica Papaya (Papaya) Fruit Extract, Chamomilla Recutita (Matricaria) Flower Extract, Helianthus Annuus Hybrid (Sunflower Seed) Oil, Tocopherol, Citric Acid\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan style=\"mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;\"\u003e\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e","brand":"NAIF","offers":[{"title":"Default Title","offer_id":49446295404871,"sku":null,"price":16.9,"currency_code":"EUR","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0790\/6829\/9591\/files\/naif-baby-balm-75ml-548036.png?v=1741554716"},{"product_id":"naif-relaxing-bath-foam-for-baby-kids-500ml-1","title":"NAIF Relaxing Bath Foam for Baby \u0026 Kids 500ml","description":"\u003cp class=\"MsoNormal\"\u003e\u003cspan style=\"mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;\"\u003eWorry-free fun in the bath with lots of bubbles made with natural ingredients. Naif Relaxing Bath Foam for Baby \u0026amp; Kids nurtures, cleanses mildly, hydrates and promises plenty of fun.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"mso-list: l0 level1 lfo1; tab-stops: list 36.0pt;\"\u003e\u003cspan style=\"mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;\"\u003eBath foam with natural derivatives from coconut oil\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"mso-list: l0 level1 lfo1; tab-stops: list 36.0pt;\"\u003e\u003cspan style=\"mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;\"\u003eCleanses and hydrates the skin while bathing\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"mso-list: l0 level1 lfo1; tab-stops: list 36.0pt;\"\u003e\n\u003cspan style=\"mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;\"\u003eDoes not contain microplastics, mineral oils, SLES\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan style=\"mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;\"\u003e\u003c\/span\u003e\n\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003c\/ul\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan style=\"mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;\"\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eHow to use:\u003c\/strong\u003e Fill the bath and add a dash of bath foam to the bath water. Mix until you see the first bubbles appear.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"MsoNormal\"\u003e\u003cb\u003e\u003cspan style=\"mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;\"\u003eIngredients:\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/b\u003e\u003cspan style=\"mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;\"\u003e Aqua, Sodium Coco-Sulfate, Coco-Glucoside, Glycerin, Cocamidopropyl Betaine, Parfum, Hydrolyzed Wheat Protein, Gossypium Herbaceum Seed Extract, Glyceryl Oleat, Tocopherol, Hydrogenated Palm Glycerides Citrate, Sodium Levulinate, Sodium Anisate, Sodium Chloride, Glycol Distearate, Citric Acid, Sodium Hydroxide\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"MsoNormal\"\u003e\u003cspan style=\"mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;\"\u003eTube\/bottle made from recycled plastic\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e","brand":"NAIF","offers":[{"title":"Default Title","offer_id":49525867938119,"sku":null,"price":15.5,"currency_code":"EUR","in_stock":false}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0790\/6829\/9591\/files\/naif-relaxing-bath-foam-for-baby-kids-500ml-125036.png?v=1739897235"},{"product_id":"hoia-baby-cream-with-zinc-75ml","title":"HOIA Baby Cream With Zinc 75ml","description":"\u003cdiv class=\"entry-content\"\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eWhipped body cream for babies with especially soft texture is rich in unrefined shea butter, coconut oil, cocoa butter and other plant-based oils, which effectively moisturize and soften skin. This product alleviates flaky and dry skin, it contains natural zinc oxide, which helps to alleviate diaper rash, reduce redness and protect skin from environmental stress. Suitable for sensitive skin and babies.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eHow to use:\u003c\/strong\u003e Apply it on skin and massage until its absorbed into your skin. Keep the product under +25 °C.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eIngredients:\u003c\/strong\u003e \u003cspan\u003e*Butyrospermum Parkii (shea) Butter, *Cocos Nucifera (coconut) Oil, Zinc Oxide, *Theobroma Cacao (cacao) Seed Butter, *Prunus Armeniaca (apricot) Kernel Oil, *Rosa Canina (rosehip) Fruit Oil, *Camelina Sativa Seed oil, Tocopherol (E-vitamin). \u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003e*From organic farming.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eHandmade in Saaremaa\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003c\/div\u003e","brand":"HOIA","offers":[{"title":"Default Title","offer_id":50324490158407,"sku":null,"price":9.9,"currency_code":"EUR","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0790\/6829\/9591\/files\/hoia-baby-cream-with-zinc-75ml-564671.jpg?v=1739897255"},{"product_id":"hoia-baby-cream-with-coconut-75ml","title":"HOIA Baby Cream With Coconut 75ml","description":"\u003cdiv class=\"entry-content\"\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eThis body cream with especially soft texture is rich in unrefined shea butter, coconut oil, cocoa butter and other plant-based oils, which moisturize and protect your skin. Baby cream has anti-inflammatory properties and it helps to alleviate redness, flaky and dry skin leaving it soft and hydrated. This body cream is ideal for babies, pregnant women and for those with sensitive skin.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eHow to use:\u003c\/strong\u003e Apply it on skin and massage until its absorbed into your skin. Keep the product under +25 °C.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eIngredients:\u003c\/strong\u003e \u003cspan\u003eOrganic Butyrospermum Parkii Butter (shea), Organic Cocos Nucifera Oil (coconut), Organic Thebroma Cacao Seed Butter (cocoa), Organic Prunus Armeniaca (apricot) Kernel Oil, Organic Rosa Canina (rosehip) Fruit Oil, Organic Camellina Sativa Seed Oil, Tocopherol (vitamin E).\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eHandmade in Saaremaa\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003c\/div\u003e","brand":"HOIA","offers":[{"title":"Default Title","offer_id":50324545503559,"sku":null,"price":9.9,"currency_code":"EUR","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0790\/6829\/9591\/files\/hoia-baby-cream-with-coconut-75ml-214265.jpg?v=1739897250"},{"product_id":"naif-milky-bath-oil-for-baby-kids-100ml","title":"NAIF Milky Bath Oil for Baby \u0026 Kids 100ml","description":"\u003cdiv data-slate-node=\"element\" class=\"css-ss00rg\"\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eA bath oil that takes care of your baby’s skin from the first bath onwards and softens the bath water. Gently cleanses and moisturizes your (newborn) baby's skin.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eNaïf Bath Oil does not contain microplastics, mineral oils and parabens. Includes linseed oil: hydrating and suitable for sensitive skin and 100% natural.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eHow to use: \u003c\/strong\u003eFill the baby bath and add about 10 ml (a few drops) of bath oil to the bath water. Mix for a moment so that the oil is evenly distributed. For some extra care, apply a baby oil after washing your baby.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eIngredients: \u003c\/strong\u003eCaprylic\/Capric Triglyceride, Coco-Caprylate\/Caprate, Glyceryl Caprylate, Polyglyceryl-3 Palmitate, Parfum\/fragrance, Gossypium Herbaceum (Cotton) Seed Oil, Tocopherol, Helianthus Annuus (Sunflower) Seed Oil, Bisabolol\u003c\/p\u003e","brand":"NAIF","offers":[{"title":"Default Title","offer_id":50915806544199,"sku":null,"price":14.9,"currency_code":"EUR","in_stock":false}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0790\/6829\/9591\/files\/naif-milky-bath-oil-for-baby-kids-100ml-696777.png?v=1739897192"},{"product_id":"naif-soothing-baby-oil-for-baby-kids-100ml","title":"NAIF Soothing Baby Oil for Baby \u0026 Kids 100ml","description":"\u003cdiv class=\"css-ss00rg\" data-slate-node=\"element\"\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eA nice oil that nourishes the skin, absorbs quickly and is not sticky. Use it to create a warm bonding moment with your baby during a massage. \u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003eNourishes and hydrates sensitive baby skin after bath time.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eBy adding sunflower seed oil and cottonseed oil the Naïf Baby Oil helps to lock in moisture post-bath time, so the skin doesn’t get dry and the natural protective layer of your baby’s skin stays intact. \u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eHow to use: \u003c\/strong\u003eUse a few drops on the skin or in the hand and gently massage the oil in circular motions. Absorbs quickly.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eIngredients: \u003c\/strong\u003eCaprylic\/Capric Triglyceride, Coco-Caprylate\/Caprate, Parfum\/fragrance, Tocopherol, Helianthus Annuus (Sunflower) Seed Oil, Gossypium (Cotton Seed) Oil, Bisabolol\u003c\/p\u003e","brand":"NAIF","offers":[{"title":"Default Title","offer_id":50915812016455,"sku":null,"price":14.9,"currency_code":"EUR","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0790\/6829\/9591\/files\/naif-soothing-baby-oil-for-baby-kids-100ml-192649.png?v=1739897180"},{"product_id":"nurme-calming-baby-oil-100ml","title":"NURME Calming Baby Oil 100ml","description":"\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eAlmond oil gets absorbed faster in the skin which prevents dryness of skin and keeps your baby’s skin soft and moisturised. Use almond oil or baby oil for a daily massage, or applying it topically to dry patches. Very effective in treating cradle cap as it is a lighter oil that will soften scaly skin without damaging delicate new skin. Best known protection against diaper rash.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cdiv\u003e\n\u003cdiv\u003e\n\u003cstrong\u003eHow to use: \u003c\/strong\u003eUse daily for massages or use only on dry spots. Can also be used in bath water. \u003cspan\u003eVery effective in treating cradle cap. Massage gently on baby's head, leave it be for a little while and then brush off very gently.\u003c\/span\u003e\n\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003cdiv\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003cdiv\u003e\n\u003cstrong\u003eIngredients:\u003c\/strong\u003e \u003cspan\u003ePrunus Amygdalis Dulcis (Sweet Almond) Oil*. \u003c\/span\u003e\n\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003cdiv\u003e\u003cspan\u003e*Organic\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003c!----\u003e","brand":"Nurme","offers":[{"title":"Default Title","offer_id":50915961995591,"sku":null,"price":11.5,"currency_code":"EUR","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0790\/6829\/9591\/files\/nurme-calming-baby-oil-100ml-165192.webp?v=1739897163"},{"product_id":"nurme-mild-baby-body-lotion-150ml","title":"NURME Mild Baby Body Lotion 150ml","description":"\u003cdiv\u003eBaby skin is soft and delicate. It is more sensitive than adult skin and can easily become dry, painful, and flaky. Nurme baby series products, including the baby body lotion, help take care of your baby’s delicate skin.\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003cdiv\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003cdiv\u003eMoisturizing and softening baby body milk is specially designed for delicate and sensitive skin. Body lotion is safe for everyday use because it is completely free of chemicals and fragrances. This protects the baby’s skin from dryness and flaking. Soothes the skin and supports its natural protective function.\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003cdiv\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003cdiv\u003eBaby body milk is rich in vitamins and fats, which are important for keeping baby’s skin healthy. The fast-absorbing consistency ensures good absorption and makes it easy to apply.\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003cdiv\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003cdiv\u003e\n\u003cdiv\u003e\n\u003cstrong\u003eHow to use: \u003cspan\u003e \u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/strong\u003eApply a small amount of body milk, preferably after washing, to the desired area of ​​skin and rub gently with massaging movements until the body milk is absorbed.\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003cdiv\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003cdiv\u003e\n\u003cstrong\u003eIngredients:\u003c\/strong\u003e \u003cspan\u003eAqua, Helianthus Annuus (Sunflower) Seed Oil*, Cocos Nucifera (Coconut) Oil*, Butyrospermum Parkii*, Glyceryl Stearate, Glycerin, Theobroma Cacao (Cocoa) Seed Butter*, Coco Glucoside, Sucrose Stearate, Coconut Alcohol, Rosa Canina (Rosehip) Fruit Oil*, Prunus Amygdalus Dulcis (Almond) Oil*, Aloe Barbadensis Leaf Juice Powder*, Tocopherol, Xanthan Gum, Benzyl Alcohol, Dehydroacetic Acid. 80.87% Certified Organic Ingredients. \u003c\/span\u003e\n\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003cdiv\u003e\u003cspan\u003e*Organic.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003c!----\u003e","brand":"Nurme","offers":[{"title":"Default Title","offer_id":50915979723079,"sku":null,"price":10.5,"currency_code":"EUR","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0790\/6829\/9591\/files\/nurme-mild-baby-body-lotion-150ml-388686.webp?v=1739897168"},{"product_id":"nurme-multipurpuse-baby-balm-50ml","title":"NURME Multipurpose Baby Balm 50ml","description":"\u003cdiv\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eA multi-purpose balm created for your baby’s delicate skin. This emollient can be used on lips, face, body, or as diaper cream and massage balm, leaving skin pampered anywhere, anytime. The Baby Balm has been formulated following strict ECOCERT principles, using only organic ingredients and excluding any fragrance or chemical ingredients.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eIt is particularly indispensable during the winter season, when sleeping in a pram, walking or playing outdoors, the cold can often make a child’s skin red and rough. Baby Balm is nourishing and provides excellent protection against cold damage. \u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eIn summer, a multi-action baby cream is helpful if the sun has made your toddler’s skin red or if mosquito bites itch and become inflamed. It’s also a great nappy cream – gentle and nourishing, it prevents and treats nappy rashes.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003cdiv\u003e\n\u003cdiv\u003e\n\u003cstrong\u003eHow to use: \u003cspan\u003e \u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/strong\u003eUse in small quantities. Massage a small amount of Baby Balm carefully onto the desired area of the skin.\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003cdiv\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003cdiv\u003e\n\u003cstrong\u003eIngredients:\u003c\/strong\u003e Butyrospermum Parkii (Shea) Butter*, Butyrospermum Parkii (Shea) Oil, Tocopherol (Vitamin-E).\n\u003cp\u003e*Organic\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003c!----\u003e","brand":"Nurme","offers":[{"title":"Default Title","offer_id":50915985359175,"sku":null,"price":9.9,"currency_code":"EUR","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0790\/6829\/9591\/files\/nurme-multipurpose-baby-balm-50ml-881507.webp?v=1739897161"},{"product_id":"nurme-mild-baby-shampoo-body-wash-200ml","title":"NURME Mild Baby Shampoo \u0026 Body Wash 200ml","description":"\u003cp\u003eThe Baby Shampoo \u0026amp; Shower Gel is a gentle cleanser that is particularly suitable for sensitive skin and can be used to wash the baby from their very first bath. The shampoo\/shower gel contains natural wheat protein and moisturizes the skin even during dry winter months. Organic and plant-based ingredients work like magic, nourishing the skin and cleansing the child from head to tiny toes.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eBaby skin is soft and delicate. It is more sensitive than adult skin and can easily become dry, painful, and flaky.\u003cspan\u003e \u003c\/span\u003eIt is essential to use specially formulated products for infants to protect their delicate skin from damage.\u003cspan\u003e \u003c\/span\u003eNurme Baby Range products, including the Baby Shampoo \u0026amp; Shower Gel, help care for a baby’s delicate skin.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eOf course, this cleansing product can also be used by all other family members, especially those with sensitive skin!\u003cspan\u003e Nurme Baby Shampoo \u0026amp; Shower Gel, with its pure composition, is very gentle on the skin while being effective.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cdiv\u003e\n\u003cdiv\u003e\n\u003cstrong\u003eHow to use: \u003c\/strong\u003eApply a small amount of shampoo\/shower gel to a washcloth or palm and gently massage the baby’s head and body. Rinse with water afterward. If the product gets into the eyes, rinse thoroughly with water.\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003cdiv\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003cdiv\u003e\n\u003cstrong\u003eIngredients:\u003c\/strong\u003e \u003cspan\u003eAqua*, Coco-Glucoside*, Sodium Coco-Sulfate*, Coco-Glucoside (and) Glyceryl Oleate*, Hydrolyzed Wheat Protein*, Sodium Benzoate (and) Potassium Sorbate*, Citric Acid*, Sodium Chloride*. \u003c\/span\u003e\n\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003cdiv\u003e\u003cspan\u003e*Natural cosmetics approved ingredient, organic.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003c!----\u003e","brand":"Nurme","offers":[{"title":"Default Title","offer_id":50915990241607,"sku":null,"price":9.9,"currency_code":"EUR","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0790\/6829\/9591\/files\/nurme-mild-baby-shampoo-body-wash-200ml-327281.webp?v=1739897183"},{"product_id":"sokind-love-lines-emollient-stretch-mark-balm-200ml","title":"SoKind Love Lines Emollient Stretch Mark Balm 200ml","description":"\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eThe consistency of Love Lines is loved by our customers and can best be described as an airy souffle. The clear effect on stretch marks, combined with the ability to ensure moisture and elasticity, makes Love Lines a product many customers return to again and again.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eNaturally formulated Stretch Mark Balm with the effective, active ingredient Regestril™, which prevents and visibly repairs stretch marks.\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003eRegistril™, consisting of lima bean extracts and peptides, works by lightening pigmentation and repairing the skin in and around stretch marks, making them far less visible. At the same time, the peptides stimulate collagen production so that the firmness of the skin improves and repairs and smoothes the damaged tissue, which also makes the product perfect for cesarean sections.\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003eAloe vera, shea butter, and shorea butter ensure soft and well-moisturized skin and improve elasticity. SoKind has selected antioxidants from vitamin E and sea buckthorn, which have a healing effect and an anti-inflammatory effect on the stretch marks and the surrounding skin.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eHow to use:\u003c\/strong\u003e Apply generously to strech mark prone skin, morning and evening.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eIngredients:\u003c\/strong\u003e Aqua, Aloe Barbadensis (Aloe Vera) Leaf Juice*, Pentylene Glycol, Cetyl Palmitate, Coco-Caprylate\/Caprate, Shorea Stenoptera (Sal) Seed Butter, Glycerin*, Cetyl Alcohol, Butyrospermum Parkii (Shea) Butter*, Simmondsia Chinensis (Jojoba) Seed Oil*, Butylene Glycol, Glyceryl Stearate Citrate, Palmitoyl Tripeptide-1, Palmitoyl Tetrapeptide-7, Phaseolus Lunatus Seed Extract, Rutin, Caprylyl Glycol, Tocopherol, Hippophae Rhamnoides (Sea Buckthorn) Fruit Juice, Cetearyl Olivate, Xanthan Gum, Cetyl Hydroxyethylcellulose, Dipotassium Phosphate, Sorbitan Olivate, Sodium Gluconate, Citric Acid, Lactic Acid, Sodium Benzoate, Potassium Sorbate.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003e*organic ingredient\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e","brand":"SoKind","offers":[{"title":"Default Title","offer_id":51062026797383,"sku":"","price":64.0,"currency_code":"EUR","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0790\/6829\/9591\/files\/sokind-love-lines-emollient-stretch-mark-balm-200ml-933477.png?v=1739897159"},{"product_id":"sokind-pure-kindness-repairing-multi-product-30ml","title":"SoKind Pure Kindness Repairing Multi-product 30ml","description":"\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eA natural, preventive, and moisturizing multi-product that protects, heals, soothes, and rebuilds chapped, cracked, and dry skin anywhere on your own or your baby's skin.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003cspan\u003eIt has been specially developed to be used in connection with breastfeeding as both a preventive and repairing nipple balm that does not need to be washed off before the baby is breastfed.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003cspan\u003ePure Kindness is formulated with Nordic Saltwort, which is particularly known for its moisture-binding properties and ability to create a protective barrier. Saltwort helps to reduce redness and irritation and balances the skin's natural pH value while also having anti-inflammatory properties.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003cspan\u003eThe Nordic Saltwort is combined with fatty acid-containing oils from Almonds and Avocado, which promote the skin's natural collagen production and protect and repair the skin.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eHow to use:\u003c\/strong\u003e Apply a small amount to the desired area and pat on gently. The balm can be reapplied as many times as needed. It is a leave-on balm and does not need to be washed off before nursing.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eIngredients:\u003c\/strong\u003e Ricinus Communis Seed Oil, Olus Oil, Oleic\/Linoleic\/Linolenic Polyglycerides, Persea Gratissima Oil, Cetyl Palmitate, Tribehenin, Butyrospermum Parkii Butter*, Prunus Amygdalus Dulcis Oil*, Salicornia Herbacea Extract, Caprylic\/Capric Triglyceride, Tocopheryl Acetate, Tocopherol\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003e*organic ingredient\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e","brand":"SoKind","offers":[{"title":"Default Title","offer_id":51062031221063,"sku":null,"price":42.0,"currency_code":"EUR","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0790\/6829\/9591\/files\/sokind-pure-kindness-repairing-multi-product-30ml-665242.png?v=1739897159"},{"product_id":"naif-mineral-sunscreen-0-perfume-spf50-for-baby-kids-100ml","title":"NAIF Mineral Sunscreen 0% Perfume for Baby \u0026 Kids SPF50 100ml","description":"\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eMineral Sunscreen SPF50 is sunscreen for Baby \u0026amp; Kids. The zinc oxide based UV filter protects the skin immediately with minimum risk of skin irritation. \u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eThe sunscreen contains zinc-oxide: a natural ingredient that adds a protective layer on top of the skin which reflects sunbeams. The sunscreen also does not contain added perfume, which makes it suitable for even the most sensitive skin. This results in immediate effectiveness against UVA and UVB radiation. The added natural oils make application easy and hydrates the skin.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\u003cspan data-sheets-root=\"1\" data-sheets-value='{\"1\":2,\"2\":\"Protects immediately against UVA and UVB radiation for baby- and kids skin\"}' data-sheets-userformat='{\"2\":15327,\"3\":{\"1\":0},\"4\":{\"1\":3,\"3\":2},\"5\":{\"1\":[{\"1\":2,\"2\":0,\"5\":{\"1\":2,\"2\":0}},{\"1\":0,\"2\":0,\"3\":3},{\"1\":1,\"2\":0,\"4\":1}]},\"6\":{\"1\":[{\"1\":2,\"2\":0,\"5\":{\"1\":2,\"2\":0}},{\"1\":0,\"2\":0,\"3\":3},{\"1\":1,\"2\":0,\"4\":1}]},\"7\":{\"1\":[{\"1\":2,\"2\":0,\"5\":{\"1\":2,\"2\":0}},{\"1\":0,\"2\":0,\"3\":3},{\"1\":1,\"2\":0,\"4\":1}]},\"9\":0,\"10\":0,\"11\":4,\"12\":0,\"14\":{\"1\":2,\"2\":0},\"15\":\"Calibri\",\"16\":11}'\u003eProtects immediately against UVA and UVB radiation for baby- and kids skin\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\u003cspan data-sheets-userformat='{\"2\":15359,\"3\":{\"1\":0},\"4\":{\"1\":3,\"3\":2},\"5\":{\"1\":[{\"1\":2,\"2\":0,\"5\":{\"1\":2,\"2\":0}},{\"1\":0,\"2\":0,\"3\":3},{\"1\":1,\"2\":0,\"4\":1}]},\"6\":{\"1\":[{\"1\":2,\"2\":0,\"5\":{\"1\":2,\"2\":0}},{\"1\":0,\"2\":0,\"3\":3},{\"1\":1,\"2\":0,\"4\":1}]},\"7\":{\"1\":[{\"1\":2,\"2\":0,\"5\":{\"1\":2,\"2\":0}},{\"1\":0,\"2\":0,\"3\":3},{\"1\":1,\"2\":0,\"4\":1}]},\"8\":{\"1\":[{\"1\":2,\"2\":0,\"5\":{\"1\":2,\"2\":0}},{\"1\":0,\"2\":0,\"3\":3},{\"1\":1,\"2\":0,\"4\":1}]},\"9\":0,\"10\":0,\"11\":4,\"12\":0,\"14\":{\"1\":2,\"2\":0},\"15\":\"Calibri\",\"16\":11}' data-sheets-value='{\"1\":2,\"2\":\"Water-resistant formula\"}' data-sheets-root=\"1\"\u003eWater-resistant formula\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\u003cspan data-sheets-userformat='{\"2\":15359,\"3\":{\"1\":0},\"4\":{\"1\":3,\"3\":2},\"5\":{\"1\":[{\"1\":2,\"2\":0,\"5\":{\"1\":2,\"2\":0}},{\"1\":0,\"2\":0,\"3\":3},{\"1\":1,\"2\":0,\"4\":1}]},\"6\":{\"1\":[{\"1\":2,\"2\":0,\"5\":{\"1\":2,\"2\":0}},{\"1\":0,\"2\":0,\"3\":3},{\"1\":1,\"2\":0,\"4\":1}]},\"7\":{\"1\":[{\"1\":2,\"2\":0,\"5\":{\"1\":2,\"2\":0}},{\"1\":0,\"2\":0,\"3\":3},{\"1\":1,\"2\":0,\"4\":1}]},\"8\":{\"1\":[{\"1\":2,\"2\":0,\"5\":{\"1\":2,\"2\":0}},{\"1\":0,\"2\":0,\"3\":3},{\"1\":1,\"2\":0,\"4\":1}]},\"9\":0,\"10\":0,\"11\":4,\"12\":0,\"14\":{\"1\":2,\"2\":0},\"15\":\"Calibri\",\"16\":11}' data-sheets-value='{\"1\":2,\"2\":\"Water-resistant formula\"}' data-sheets-root=\"1\"\u003eDermatologically tested, 0% perfume for extra sensitive skin\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003c\/ul\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eHow to use: \u003c\/strong\u003e\u003cspan\u003eShake the sunscreen before use. Apply a generous amount evenly to the body and face before your kids go in the sun. Reapply every two hours and after swimming for optimum protection. Do not keep product in the sun.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eIngredients:\u003c\/strong\u003e \u003cspan\u003eCaprylic\/Capric Triglyceride, Decyl Oleate, Zinc Oxide, Hydrogenated Vegetable Oil, Caprylic\/Capric\/Myristic\/Stearic Triglyceride, Dextrin Palmitate, Coco-Caprylate\/Caprate, Triheptanoin, Ricinus Communis Seed Oil, Bis-Ethylhexyloxyphenol Methoxyphenyl Triazine, Cocos Nucifera Oil, Polyhydroxystearic Acid, Allantoin, Tocopherol, Palmitic Acid, Helianthus Annuus Seed Oil, Oryzanol, Bisabolol, Pongamol\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eTube made from recycled plastic\u003c\/p\u003e","brand":"NAIF","offers":[{"title":"Default Title","offer_id":51084419760455,"sku":null,"price":22.9,"currency_code":"EUR","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0790\/6829\/9591\/files\/naif-mineral-sunscreen-0-perfume-for-baby-kids-spf50-100ml-633941.png?v=1741554339"},{"product_id":"naif-mineral-sunscreen-stick-0-perfume-for-baby-kids-spf50-36g","title":"NAIF Mineral Sunscreen Stick 0% Perfume for Baby \u0026 Kids SPF50 36g","description":"\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eMineral Sunscreen Stick SPF50 is a sunscreen for Baby \u0026amp; Kids. The zinc oxide based UV filter protects the skin immediately with minimum risk of skin irritation. Easy to take and to apply, even by kids who want to do everything themselves. Without added perfume and suitable for sensitive skin.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eThe sunscreen contains zinc-oxide: a natural ingredient that adds a protective layer on top of the skin which reflects sunbeams. This results in immediate effectiveness against UVA and UVB radiation.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\u003cspan\u003eProtects immediately against UVA and UVB radiation for baby- and kids skin\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\u003cspan\u003eWater-resistant formula\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\n\u003cspan\u003eDermatologically tested, 0% perfume for extra sensitive skin\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\n\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003c\/ul\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eHow to use: \u003c\/strong\u003eApply a generous amount to the body and face before your kids go in the sun. Make sure to spread it well. Reapply every two hours and after swimming for maximum protection\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eIngredients:\u003c\/strong\u003e \u003cspan\u003eCaprylic\/Capric\/Myristic\/Stearic Triglyceride, Zinc Oxide, Helianthus Annuus Seed Cera, Hydrogenated Rapeseed Oil, Tocopherol, Pongamol, Helianthus Annuus Seed Oil, Ascorbyl Palmitate\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eTube made from recycled plastic\u003c\/p\u003e","brand":"NAIF","offers":[{"title":"Default Title","offer_id":51084446499143,"sku":null,"price":14.9,"currency_code":"EUR","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0790\/6829\/9591\/files\/naif-mineral-sunscreen-stick-0-perfume-for-baby-kids-spf50-36g-964551.png?v=1741554338"},{"product_id":"naif-lotion-baby-wipes-54pcs","title":"NAIF Lotion Baby Wipes 54pcs","description":"\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eNaïf plastic-free lotion wipes are everything you would expect from a baby wipe: strong, well moisturized, with ingredients that take good care of the sensitive baby skin. Does not include polyester fibers and microplastics. Also suitable as a nose cleaner.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003cspan\u003eBy using extra (vegetable) glycerin, aloe vera and bamboo for extra hydration and prematurely soothing red baby bottoms. The lotion has been dermatologically tested and does not contain alcohol, perfume or other ingredients that can cause red baby's buttocks.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eHow to use: \u003c\/strong\u003eWhile changing, open the package with one hand, holding your baby with the other. Wipe the area well and don't forget the folds. When finished, close the package tightly to prevent dehydration.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eIngredients:\u003c\/strong\u003e \u003cspan\u003eAqua, Glycerin, Bambusa Arundinacea Stem (Bamboo) Extract, Sodium Cocoyl Glutamate, Levulinic Acid, Aloe Barbadensis (Aloe Vera) Leaf Juice Powder, Sodium Benzoate, Citric Acid\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e","brand":"NAIF","offers":[{"title":"Default Title","offer_id":51084485984583,"sku":null,"price":3.95,"currency_code":"EUR","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0790\/6829\/9591\/files\/naif-lotion-baby-wipes-54pcs-938646.jpg?v=1740228550"},{"product_id":"luuv-natural-kids-shower-foam-150ml","title":"LUUV Natural Kids Shower Foam 150ml","description":"\u003cp\u003eThis is LUUV kids shower foam – the ultimate bath-time companion that brings joy, playfulness, and eco-consciousness to your little one’s daily routine! Certified with the leading ECOCERT \/ COSMOS eco-certificate, this delightful foam will make showering an adventure filled with laughter and fun.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eWe understand that your child’s delicate skin deserves only the best, which is why this shower foam is crafted from carefully selected detergents that are gentle and won’t irritate your child’s precious skin. The sweet and juicy pear aroma is completely derived from natural sources, ensuring a captivating scent without any allergens. As for the vibrant pinkish purple color, a surprising secret ingredient is used – potato extract! That’s right, this eco-certified formula uses this natural wonder to create a mesmerizing hue that will captivate your child’s imagination. It’s like a burst of colorful magic in every pump!\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eNatural and allergen-free\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eFresh pear scent\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eDoes not irritate or dry skin\u003cbr\u003e\n\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003c\/ul\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003enatural | cruelty free | sustainable | vegan | certified\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eThe product is made in Estonia\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"MsoNormal\"\u003e\u003cb\u003e\u003cspan style=\"mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;\"\u003eHow to use:\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/b\u003e\u003cspan style=\"mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;\"\u003e \u003cspan\u003eApply the shower gel on damp skin with light circular movements, rinse and dry.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"MsoNormal\"\u003e\u003cb\u003e\u003cspan style=\"mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;\"\u003eIngredients:\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/b\u003e\u003cspan style=\"mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;\"\u003e \u003cspan\u003eAqua, Cocamidopropyl Betaine, Glycerin, Coco-Glucoside, Ipomoea Batatas (Potato) Root Extract, Cetyl Alcohol, Sodium Benzoate, Potassium Sorbate, Citric Acid, Aroma, Acacia Senegal Gum, Maltodextrin\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e","brand":"LUUV","offers":[{"title":"Default Title","offer_id":51111034487111,"sku":null,"price":10.9,"currency_code":"EUR","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0790\/6829\/9591\/files\/luuv-natural-kids-shower-foam-150ml-609563.png?v=1740891412"},{"product_id":"luuv-natural-kids-shampoo-250ml","title":"LUUV Natural Kids Shampoo 250ml","description":"\u003cp\u003eLUUV natural kids shampoo  – where fun meets healthy hair! This shampoo takes your child’s hair care to new heights with its completely natural, tear-free formula. Designed for little adventurers, it leaves hair strong, shiny, and gently detangles even the most resistant knots. With ECOCERT\/COSMOS eco-certificate, you can trust that LUUV kids shampoo is not only gentle on your little one’s hair but also on the environment.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eCarefully selected herbal detergents are perfect for your child’s delicate scalp, ensuring a nurturing and soothing wash. Shampoo is also infused with the goodness of moisturizing aloe and plant betaine – not only does it make their hair easy to comb, but it also strengthens it from root to tip, leaving it looking healthy, vibrant, and ready for any adventure that comes their way. The sweet and juicy pear aroma is naturally derived and allergen-free. LUUV natural kids shampoo is not only natural but also vegan, making it a choice you can feel great about. Experience hair that’s as soft as a mother’s caress and join the fun today!\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eNatural and allergen-free\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eTear-free formula\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eFresh pear scent\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eDoes not irritate skin\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eECOCERT\/COSMOS certified\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eNatural origin 98,4%\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003c\/ul\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003enatural | cruelty free | sustainable | vegan | certified\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eThe product is made in Estonia\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"MsoNormal\"\u003e\u003cb\u003e\u003cspan style=\"mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;\"\u003eHow to use:\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/b\u003e\u003cspan style=\"mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;\"\u003e \u003cspan\u003eApply the shampoo thoroughly on wet hair. Massage into a lather. Rinse. Repeat the procedure, if necessary.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"MsoNormal\"\u003e\u003cb\u003e\u003cspan style=\"mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;\"\u003eIngredients:\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/b\u003e\u003cspan style=\"mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;\"\u003e \u003cspan\u003eAqua, Coco-Glucoside, Sodium Lauryl Glucose Carboxylate, Lauryl Glucoside, Oryza Sativa (Rice) Starch, Aloe Barbadensis Leaf Juice, Betaine, Guar Hydroxypropyltrimonium Chloride, Citric Acid, Glyceryl Oleate, Hydrolyzed Wheat Protein, Sodium Benzoate, Potassium Sorbate, Aroma\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e","brand":"LUUV","offers":[{"title":"Default Title","offer_id":51115336728903,"sku":null,"price":11.5,"currency_code":"EUR","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0790\/6829\/9591\/files\/luuv-natural-kids-shampoo-250ml-163262.png?v=1740891417"},{"product_id":"luuv-natural-kids-bubble-bath-200ml","title":"LUUV Natural Kids Bubble Bath 200ml","description":"\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eTransform your child’s bath time into a delightful adventure with LUUV pear bath foam for kids! This incredible bath foam is not only certified with the prestigious ECOCERT \/ COSMOS eco-certificate, but it also adds a touch of magic and excitement to every bathing experience. The rich and velvety soft foam, derived from carefully selected herbal detergents, caresses your little one’s delicate skin without causing any irritation or dryness. And the delicious pear aroma? It’s all-natural, creating a truly mouth-watering bathing experience.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eNatural and allergen-free\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eFresh pear scent\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eDoes not irritate or dry skin\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eECOCERT\/COSMOS certified\u003cbr\u003e\n\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eNatural origin 98,72%\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003c\/ul\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003enatural | cruelty free | sustainable | vegan | certified\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eThe product is made in Estonia\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"MsoNormal\"\u003e\u003cb\u003e\u003cspan style=\"mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;\"\u003eHow to use:\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/b\u003e\u003cspan style=\"mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;\"\u003e \u003cspan\u003eJust add this magical foam to warm running water, and let the enchanting bath time adventure begin!\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"MsoNormal\"\u003e\u003cb\u003e\u003cspan style=\"mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;\"\u003eIngredients:\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/b\u003e\u003cspan style=\"mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;\"\u003e \u003cspan\u003eAqua, Coco-Glucoside, Sodium Coco-Sulfate, Cocamidopropyl Betaine, Aroma, Glyceryl Oleate, Sodium Benzoate, Potassium Sorbate, Citric Acid\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e","brand":"LUUV","offers":[{"title":"Default Title","offer_id":51115356291399,"sku":null,"price":11.0,"currency_code":"EUR","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0790\/6829\/9591\/files\/luuv-natural-kids-bubble-bath-200ml-677435.png?v=1740891419"},{"product_id":"luuv-natural-kids-detangling-spray-100ml","title":"LUUV Natural Kids Detangling Spray 100ml","description":"\u003cp\u003eCertified with the globally recognized ECOCERT\/COSMOS certification, this spray is a game-changer for your little one’s hair care routine. It’s time to say goodbye to stubborn tangles and hello to hassle-free styling!\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eLUUV Detangle spray is specially formulated to tame even the most stubborn knots, leaving your little one’s hair silky smooth, strong, and oh-so-shiny! And let’s not forget the delightful scent! Detangling spray comes with a mouthwatering juicy pear scent that kids absolutely adore. Plus, you can rest easy knowing that the scent is naturally derived and free from any allergens. Your little one’s hair is in good hands. And now that your little one’s hair is tangle-free, it’s time to explore a whole new world of hairstyles! From cute pigtails to stylish braids, this spray opens up endless possibilities for your child’s hair adventures.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eNatural and allergen-free\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eFresh pear scent\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eDoes not irritate skin\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eECOCERT\/COSMOS certified\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eNatural origin 99,76%\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003c\/ul\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003enatural | cruelty free | sustainable | vegan | certified\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eThe product is made in Estonia\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"MsoNormal\"\u003e\u003cb\u003e\u003cspan style=\"mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;\"\u003eHow to use:\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/b\u003e\u003cspan style=\"mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;\"\u003e \u003cspan\u003eShake the bottle before use. Spray the conditioner on the hair, let it work for a few moments and comb through the hair. Can be used both on wet hair after washing and on dry hair daily.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"MsoNormal\"\u003e\u003cb\u003e\u003cspan style=\"mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;\"\u003eIngredients:\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/b\u003e\u003cspan style=\"mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;\"\u003e \u003cspan\u003eAqua, Cetearyl Alcohol, Lecithin, Sodium Cetearyl Sulfate, Olus Oil, Propanediol, Betaine, Coconut Alkanes, Sodium Benzoate, Potassium Sorbate, Citric Acid, Aroma\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e","brand":"LUUV","offers":[{"title":"Default Title","offer_id":51115375034695,"sku":null,"price":14.0,"currency_code":"EUR","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0790\/6829\/9591\/files\/luuv-natural-kids-detangling-spray-100ml-412749.png?v=1740891417"},{"product_id":"luuv-magnesium-cream-200ml","title":"LUUV Magnesium Cream 200ml","description":"\u003cp\u003eIntroducing uplifting and rejuvenating LUUV Magnesium Cream – your gateway to a world of wellness and relaxation.  Certified with the prestigious ECOCERT\/COSMOS eco-certificate, this Magnesium Cream is a trusted and sustainable choice for your well-being. With daily use, it becomes your partner in preventing and reducing magnesium deficiency, while providing relief from muscle aches and tensions. Harnessing the power of magnesium chloride, it offers a transdermal method of absorption, allowing your body to benefit from this vital mineral in the fastest and most efficient way. \u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eThis cream is infused with the goodness of coconut oil, a natural emollient that closely resembles your skin’s own lipids. This dynamic duo ensures that even those with dry skin can absorb magnesium effectively, while providing deep hydration and nourishment. Plus, it’s suitable for even the most sensitive skin, ensuring a gentle and soothing experience for all. \u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eFor everyday use\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003ePrevents\/reduces magnesium deficiency\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eRelieves muscle pain and tension\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eMoisturizing and nourishing\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eFor the whole family\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eSuitable during pregnancy\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eECOCERT\/COSMOS\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eBeauty Shortlist Awards 2024- Wellbeing Category Gold medal\u003cbr\u003e\n\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003c\/ul\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"\u003eKey ingredients: \u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli id=\"tw-target-text\" class=\"tw-data-text tw-text-large tw-ta\" dir=\"ltr\" data-placeholder=\"Tõlge\" aria-label=\"Tõlgitud tekst\" data-ved=\"2ahUKEwi-ruvxp7CGAxVrExAIHSOFDeAQ3ewLegQIBRAU\"\u003e\u003cspan class=\"Y2IQFc\" lang=\"en\"\u003e\u003cspan style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"\u003eMagnesium\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e \u003c\/span\u003ehelps muscles to relax, muscle spasms are caused by lack of magnesium. Post-workout, transdermal magnesium is best because it’s topical (you apply it to the area that strained the muscles). There are no side effects when taking topical magnesium and the effect is immediate.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli class=\"tw-data-text tw-text-large tw-ta\" dir=\"ltr\" data-placeholder=\"Tõlge\" aria-label=\"Tõlgitud tekst\" data-ved=\"2ahUKEwi-ruvxp7CGAxVrExAIHSOFDeAQ3ewLegQIBRAU\"\u003e\u003cspan class=\"Y2IQFc\" lang=\"en\"\u003e\u003cspan style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"\u003eCoconut oil\u003c\/span\u003e\/coconut fat is the lightest of solid fats. With good absorption and blends well into the skin, nourishing but not heavy. Is very similar to the lipids in our own skin, so human skin absorbs it well.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli class=\"tw-data-text tw-text-large tw-ta\" dir=\"ltr\" data-placeholder=\"Tõlge\" aria-label=\"Tõlgitud tekst\" data-ved=\"2ahUKEwi-ruvxp7CGAxVrExAIHSOFDeAQ3ewLegQIBRAU\"\u003e\u003cspan class=\"Y2IQFc\" lang=\"en\"\u003e\u003cspan style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"\u003eLemon essential oil\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e \u003c\/span\u003eis used to perfume the product, but it also has strong detox properties. Mild enough with a pleasant citrus scent. It is well suited for anti-cellulite products and for boosting the skin. Strengthens the immune system.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003c\/ul\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003enatural | cruelty free | sustainable | vegan | certified | paraben free\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eThe product is made in Estonia\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"MsoNormal\"\u003e\u003cb\u003e\u003cspan style=\"mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;\"\u003eHow to use:\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/b\u003e\u003cspan style=\"mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;\"\u003e \u003cspan\u003eMagnesium cream is suitable for use by the whole family and is also safe for pregnant women to use. It wonderfully helps relieve muscle tension after exercise and prevents and reduces magnesium deficiency in the body. In children, it helps relieve discomfort caused by growing pains. The cream contains magnesium chloride, which is best absorbed through the skin and also the fastest way to reduce magnesium deficiency.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"MsoNormal\"\u003e\u003cb\u003e\u003cspan style=\"mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;\"\u003eIngredients:\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/b\u003e\u003cspan style=\"mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;\"\u003e \u003cspan\u003eAqua, Magnesium Chloride , Cocos Nucifera Oil, Polyglyceryl-3 Distearate, Glyceryl Stearate Citrate , Glyceryl stearate SE, Citrus Limon Peel (Lemon) Oil, Cymbopogon Flexuosus (Lemongrass) Oil, Mentha Piperita (Peppermint) Oil, Triethyl Citrate, Glyceryl Caprylate, Xanthan gum, Benzoic Acid, Citral, Limonene\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e","brand":"LUUV","offers":[{"title":"Default Title","offer_id":51115523342663,"sku":null,"price":17.0,"currency_code":"EUR","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0790\/6829\/9591\/files\/luuv-magnesium-cream-200ml-418252.png?v=1740560025"},{"product_id":"naif-milky-bath-oil-for-baby-kids-100ml-copy","title":"Petit\u0026Jolie Bath Oil 200ml","description":"\u003cdiv class=\"css-ss00rg\" data-slate-node=\"element\"\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003ePetit\u0026amp;Jolie Bath Oil gently cleanses the skin during the bath. The rich emulsion has a very caring effect, so that baby's skin feels soft and supple after the bath. This makes the bath oil suitable for babies with (very) dry skin.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003cspan\u003eThe Bath Oil is made from 100% natural ingredients. So the oil does not contain parabens, paraffin, SLS or synthetic fragrances or dyes.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003cspan\u003eThe Bath Oil can be used directly from birth. But older children and adults can of course also use the bath oil very well.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003cspan\u003eThe packaging is made from 100% recycled plastic.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eHow to use: \u003c\/strong\u003eWhile filling the baby bath tub, add a little bath oil and stir with your hand.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eIngredients: \u003c\/strong\u003eGlycerin, Helianthus Annuus Hybrid Oil*, Polyglyceryl-5 Oleate, Parfum**, Rosmarinus Officinalis Leaf Extract*, Helianthus Annuus Seed Oil\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e* from organic source \u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e**natural essential oils\u003c\/p\u003e","brand":"Petit \u0026 Jolie","offers":[{"title":"Default Title","offer_id":51133583589703,"sku":null,"price":10.5,"currency_code":"EUR","in_stock":false}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0790\/6829\/9591\/files\/petitjolie-bath-oil-200ml-845366.png?v=1740808671"},{"product_id":"petit-joliehair-body-shampoo-200ml","title":"Petit\u0026Jolie Hair \u0026 Body Shampoo 200ml","description":"\u003cdiv data-slate-node=\"element\" class=\"css-ss00rg\"\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003ePetit\u0026amp;Jolie Hair\u0026amp;Body Shampoo cleanses and cares for the skin and hair in a mild way. The special composition ensures supple skin and prevents dehydration. \u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003eThe shampoo is suitable for children with dry and sensitive skin. \u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003eIt doesn't sting the eyes.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003cspan\u003eLike all our products, the baby hair \u0026amp; body shampoo does not contain parabens, SLS, paraffin or synthetic fragrances and dyes. The baby shampoo is made from 100% natural ingredients.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003cspan\u003eThe bottle is made from 100% recycled plastic.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eHow to use: \u003c\/strong\u003eWhile taking a shower or bath, add a small amount of shampoo to your hand or washcloth and lightly massage the skin and hair of your baby. Rinse well with water afterwards.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eIngredients: \u003c\/strong\u003eAqua, Glycerin, Sodium Cocoyl Glutamate, Coco-Glucoside, Decyl Glucoside, Xanthan Gum, Glyceryl Oleate, Parfum*, Dicaprylyl Ether, Sodium Anisate, Sodium Levulinate\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e* natural essential oils\u003c\/p\u003e","brand":"Petit \u0026 Jolie","offers":[{"title":"Default Title","offer_id":51133856514375,"sku":null,"price":8.9,"currency_code":"EUR","in_stock":false}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0790\/6829\/9591\/files\/petitjolie-hair-body-shampoo-200ml-339984.png?v=1740808671"},{"product_id":"petit-jolie-nourishing-cream-75ml","title":"Petit\u0026Jolie Nourishing Cream 75ml","description":"\u003cdiv data-slate-node=\"element\" class=\"css-ss00rg\"\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003ePetit\u0026amp;Jolie Oily Cream is a nourishing and moisturizing cream especially for the delicate (baby) skin. The cream offers extra care and protection due to the unique composition of, among other things, organically grown shea butter and almond oil. Oily Cream is very suitable for babies with dry or sensitive skin and can be used for both the face and the body.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003cspan\u003eAll ingredients are of 100% natural origin. The cream therefore contains no parabens, paraffin, synthetic fragrances and dyes.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eHow to use: \u003c\/strong\u003eApply to the baby’s skin or face daily. If the skin is getting better you can change to the bodylotion.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eIngredients: \u003c\/strong\u003eAqua (Water), Glycerin, Helianthus Annuus (Sunflower) Hybrid Oil*, Simmondsia Chinensis (Jojoba) Seed Oil*, Pentylene Glycol, Cetearyl Alcohol, Prunus Amygdalus Dulcis (Almond) Oil*, Squalane, Butyrospermum Parkii (Shea) Butter*, Cetyl Palmitate, Glyceryl Stearate Citrate, Polyglyceryl-3 Stearate, Palmitic Acid, Stearic Acid, Limnanthes Alba (Meadowfoam) Seed Oil, Sodium Polyphosphat, Jojoba Esters, Helianthus Annuus (Sunflower) Seed Wax, Acacia Decurrens Flower Wax, Polyglycerin-3, Tocopherol Dipotassium Glycyrrhizate, Helianthus Annuus (Sunflower) Seed Oil, Sodium Hyaluronate, Tocopherol, Sodium Levulinate, Xanthan Gum, Sodium Anisate, Parfum (Fragrance)**, Oryzanol\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e*organic source\u003cbr\u003e**from natrural essential oils\u003c\/p\u003e","brand":"Petit \u0026 Jolie","offers":[{"title":"Default Title","offer_id":51133923361095,"sku":null,"price":9.6,"currency_code":"EUR","in_stock":false}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0790\/6829\/9591\/files\/petitjolie-nourishing-cream-75ml-115815.png?v=1740808669"},{"product_id":"petit-jolie-diaper-cream-75ml","title":"Petit\u0026Jolie Diaper Cream 75ml","description":"\u003cdiv data-slate-node=\"element\" class=\"css-ss00rg\"\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003ePetit\u0026amp;Jolie Diaper Cream protects, restores and nourishes the skin around the diaper area. It cares for and protects the sensitive baby skin. The buttocks cream with, among other things, beeswax provides an extra layer of protection against moisture on the buttocks. The zinc oxide present has a drying effect. The unique composition of natural ingredients soothes the skin and prevents diaper rash. It makes the skin silky soft again.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003cspan\u003eThe diaper cream is perfume free and is made from 100% natural ingredients, so it contains no parabens, paraffin or synthetic fragrances and dyes.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eHow to use: \u003c\/strong\u003eApply after changing diapers\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eIngredients: \u003c\/strong\u003eAqua, Decyl Oleate, Helianthus Annuus Hybrid Oil*, Sesamum Indicum Seed Oil*, Zinc Oxide, Polyglyceryl-3 Polyricinoleate, Cera Alba*, Cetyl Ricinoleate, Sorbitan Sesquioleate, Lanolin, Magnesiumsulfate, Zinc PCA, Glyceryl Caprate, Tocopherol, Helianthus Annuus Seed Oil, Aluminium Tristearate, Magnesium Stearate, Oryzanol, Vanilla Planifolia Fruit Extract*                       \u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e* from organic source\u003c\/p\u003e","brand":"Petit \u0026 Jolie","offers":[{"title":"Default Title","offer_id":51133987324231,"sku":null,"price":8.9,"currency_code":"EUR","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0790\/6829\/9591\/files\/petitjolie-diaper-cream-75ml-385720.png?v=1740808665"},{"product_id":"petit-jolie-body-lotion-150ml","title":"Petit\u0026Jolie Body Lotion 150ml","description":"\u003cdiv data-slate-node=\"element\" class=\"css-ss00rg\"\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003ePetit\u0026amp;Jolie Body Lotion is a nourishing and moisturizing lotion especially designed for the fragile and sensitive skin of your baby. The apricot oil provides extra elasticity and a long-lasting ultra-soft skin. The body lotion is easy to spread and is quickly absorbed.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003cspan\u003eThe body lotion is 100% from natural ingredients, so it contains no parabens, paraffin or synthetic fragrances and dyes.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eHow to use: \u003c\/strong\u003eGently massage on baby's skin after washing\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eIngredients: \u003c\/strong\u003eAqua (Water), Helianthus Annuus (sunflower) Hybrid Oil*, Decyl Oleate, Glycerin, Prunus Armeniaca (apricot) Kernel Oil, Pentylene Glycol, Cetearyl Alcohol, Glyceryl Stearate Citrate, Glyceryl Caprylate, Hippophae Rhamnoides (sea buckthorn) Fruit Extract*, Chamomilla Recutita (camomile) Flower  Extrakt*, Schizandra Sphenanthera (schisandra) Fruit Extract, Rosmarinus Officinalis (rosemary)  Leaf Extract\u003cem\u003e, Salvia Officinalis (sage) Leaf Extract, Helianthus Annuus (sunflower) Seed Oil, Tocopherol, Sodium Phytate, Oryzanol, Xanthan Gum, Parfum\u003c\/em\u003e*\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e* organic source\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e**natural essential oils\u003c\/p\u003e","brand":"Petit \u0026 Jolie","offers":[{"title":"Default Title","offer_id":51134047289671,"sku":null,"price":10.5,"currency_code":"EUR","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0790\/6829\/9591\/files\/petitjolie-body-lotion-150ml-598489.png?v=1740808669"},{"product_id":"petit-jolie-massage-oi-100ml","title":"Petit\u0026Jolie Massage Oil 100ml","description":"\u003cdiv data-slate-node=\"element\" class=\"css-ss00rg\"\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003ePetit\u0026amp;Jolie Massage Oil nourishes and protects the skin and is very suitable for a baby massage, a nice relaxing moment for both of you. The ultra-soft oil consists of a combination of organically grown sunflower, jojoba and almond oils.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003cspan\u003eThe massage oil is 100% from natural ingredients and contains no paraffin or synthetic fragrances and dyes.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003cspan\u003eThe massage oil is also suitable as a skin oil (for all ages)\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eHow to use: \u003c\/strong\u003ePour a few drops of oil onto the palms of your (warm) hands and then gentle massage onto the skin of your baby.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eIngredients: \u003c\/strong\u003eHelianthus Annuus Hybrid Oil* \u003cem\u003e(sunflower),\u003c\/em\u003e Simmondsia Chinensis Seed Oil* \u003cem\u003e(jojoba),\u003c\/em\u003e Prunus Amygdalus Dulcis Oil* \u003cem\u003e(almond),\u003c\/em\u003e Schizandra Sphenanthera Fruit Extract, Tocopherol \u003cem\u003e(vitamin E),\u003c\/em\u003e Helianthus Annuus Seed Oil \u003cem\u003e(sunflower),\u003c\/em\u003e Vanilla Planifolia Fruit Extract\u003cem\u003e (vanilla), Parfum\u003c\/em\u003e*\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e* organic source  \u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e** natural essential oils\u003c\/p\u003e","brand":"Petit \u0026 Jolie","offers":[{"title":"Default Title","offer_id":51134084972871,"sku":null,"price":9.9,"currency_code":"EUR","in_stock":false}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0790\/6829\/9591\/files\/petitjolie-massage-oil-100ml-159958.png?v=1740808668"},{"product_id":"petit-jolie-calendula-balm-55ml","title":"Petit\u0026Jolie Calendula Balm 55ml","description":"\u003cdiv class=\"css-ss00rg\" data-slate-node=\"element\"\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003ePetit \u0026amp; Jolie Calendula Balm has been specially developed for irritated or chapped skin, such as cracked nipples and diaper rash. The organically grown Calendula extract has a restorative and soothing effect.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003cspan\u003eThe balm does not contain perfume and water.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003cspan\u003eThe balm consists of ingredients of 100% natural origin. It does not contain parabens, paraffin and synthetic fragrances and dyes.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eHow to use: \u003c\/strong\u003eWarm the calendula balm with your fingers. And massage the balm softly on the skin. Repeat as long as needed.\u003cstrong\u003e\u003cspan\u003e \u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/strong\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eIngredients: \u003c\/strong\u003eRicinus Communis Seed Oil, Helianthus Annuus Hybrid Oil *, Cocoglycerides, Hydrogenated Vegetable Oil, Decyl Oleate, Cera Alba, Polyglyceryl-2 Dipolyhydroxystearate, Calendula Officinalis Flower Extract *, Daucus Carota Sativa Root Extract *, Rosmarinus Officinalis Leaf Extract *, Simmondsia Chinensis Seed Oil, Capsicum Annuum Extract *, Lithospermum Erytrorhizom Root Extract, Helianthus Annuus Seed Oil, Tocopherol.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e* from organic source\u003c\/p\u003e","brand":"Petit \u0026 Jolie","offers":[{"title":"Default Title","offer_id":51134455775559,"sku":null,"price":9.9,"currency_code":"EUR","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0790\/6829\/9591\/files\/petitjolie-calendula-balm-55ml-648274.png?v=1740808673"},{"product_id":"petit-jolie-mineral-sunscreen-30spf-100ml","title":"Petit\u0026Jolie Mineral Sunscreen 30SPF 100ml","description":"\u003cdiv data-slate-node=\"element\" class=\"css-ss00rg\"\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003ePetit \u0026amp; Jolie sunscreen SPF 30 protects your skin from harmful UV rays. The cream applies easily and leaves no white cast. It contains non-nano zinc oxide as a natural sun filter.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eThe mineral sunscreen does not contain\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cstrong\u003e\u003cspan\u003e \u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/strong\u003e\u003cspan\u003eparfum.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003cspan\u003eIMPORTANT: The cream provides effective protection against UV rays, but cannot guarantee 100% protection. Keep babies and children out of direct sunlight.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eHow to use: \u003c\/strong\u003eApply a generous amount of sunscreen to the skin. Reapply frequently for optimal protection.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eIngredients: \u003c\/strong\u003eAqua (water), Zinc Oxide, Caprylic\/Capric Triglyceride, Dicaprylyl Carbonate, Pentylene Glycol, Calcium Sodium Borosilicate, Sucrose Palmitate, Polyhydroxystearic Acid, Glyceryl Stearate, Oryzanol, Sucrose Distearate, Pongamia Pinnata Seed Extract, Xanthan Gum, Sodium Stearoyl Glutamate\u003c\/p\u003e","brand":"Petit \u0026 Jolie","offers":[{"title":"Default Title","offer_id":51134480515399,"sku":null,"price":19.9,"currency_code":"EUR","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0790\/6829\/9591\/files\/petitjolie-mineral-sunscreen-30spf-100ml-844493.png?v=1740808671"},{"product_id":"naif-nurturing-day-cream-50ml-copy","title":"NAIF Cooling Aftersun 100ml","description":"\u003cdiv class=\"css-ss00rg\" data-slate-node=\"element\"\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eNaïf Cooling After Sun Gel soothes, moisturizes and restores the skin after a sunny day. Aloe Vera provides cooling and regeneration, glycerine for hydration. This keeps even the most sensitive skin soft and supple. Just what the skin needs after exposure to UV rays. Also nice: absorbs quickly and doesn't leave a sticky layer.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eHow to use: \u003c\/strong\u003eApply generously after exposure to the sun. Especially on the areas that have had a lot of sun. Repeat if skin still feels dry.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eTip: Keep the gel in the refrigerator, so it is extra cooling.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eIngredients: \u003c\/strong\u003eAqua\/Water, Glycerin, Methylpropanediol, Cetearyl Alcohol, Cetyl Alcohol, Glyceryl Stearate Citrate, Parfum\/Fragrance, Aloe Barbadensis Leaf Juice Powder, Allantoin, Caprylyl Glycol, Phenylpropanol, Xanthan Gum, Lactic Acid, Sodium Hydroxide\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eAll Naïf products are vegan, made with a mild fragrance and dermatologically tested, without the 26 most common allergens. They also do not contain SLES or microplastics. The tubes are made from sugar cane-based bioplastic.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e","brand":"NAIF","offers":[{"title":"Default Title","offer_id":52037698814279,"sku":null,"price":13.9,"currency_code":"EUR","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0790\/6829\/9591\/files\/naif-cooling-aftersun-100ml-5567632.png?v=1753967377"},{"product_id":"luuv-natural-conditioner-for-kids-200ml","title":"LUUV Natural Conditioner For Kids 200ml","description":"\u003cp\u003eThis enchanting conditioner deeply moisturizes, nourishes, and protects the hair, leaving it irresistibly shiny. LUUV children’s hair conditioner is certified with the prestigious ECOCERT\/COSMOS eco-certificate.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eSay goodbye to tangles and hello to effortlessly smooth and manageable hair! Conditioner strengthens hair from roots to ends, making it easy to comb and wonderfully lightweight. Infused with natural oils and betaine, it deeply moisturizes and enhances the overall health and beauty of the hair. And let’s not forget about that enchanting vanilla aroma! It’s derived from natural sources and is completely allergen-free. If your little one dreams of becoming the next Rapunzel with long, flowing locks, LUUV natural conditioner for kids is the perfect choice!\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eNatural and allergen-free\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eSweet vanilla scent\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eDoes not irritate skin\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eECOCERT\/COSMOS certified\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eNatural origin 98,72%\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003c\/ul\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003enatural | cruelty free | sustainable | vegan | certified\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eThe product is made in Estonia\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"MsoNormal\"\u003e\u003cb\u003e\u003cspan style=\"mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;\"\u003eHow to use:\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/b\u003e\u003cspan style=\"mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;\"\u003e  Use the conditioner after shampoo and apply from the ends only. Let it sit and rinse! You can use the conditioner after every wash.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"MsoNormal\"\u003e\u003cb\u003e\u003cspan style=\"mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;\"\u003eIngredients:\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/b\u003e\u003cspan style=\"mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;\"\u003e Aqua, Cetearyl Alcohol, Lecithin, Sodium Cetearyl Sulfate, Olus Oil, Cetyl Alcohol, Betaine, Sodium Benzoate, Potassium Sorbate, Citric Acid, Aroma\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e","brand":"LUUV","offers":[{"title":"Default Title","offer_id":52138032202055,"sku":null,"price":11.9,"currency_code":"EUR","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0790\/6829\/9591\/files\/luuv-natural-conditioner-for-kids-200ml-2844222.jpg?v=1756222791"},{"product_id":"bee-it-shampoo-body-wash-pink-for-kids-50ml","title":"BEE IT Shampoo \u0026 Body Wash Pink for Kids 50ml","description":"\u003cp class=\"MsoNormal\"\u003ePhysiological pH shampoo \u0026amp; body wash rich in natural ingredients to enjoy the bath time as a pleasant experience of play and creativity. With organic aloe vera, sweet almond oil, organic honey and propolis, for a delicate and nourishing action.\u003cbr\u003eAmused and clean, his hair will be velvety and luminous, and his skin will be even softer and more fragrant.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"MsoNormal\"\u003e\u003cb\u003eHow to use:\u003c\/b\u003e Apply to hair and body and massage gently, then rinse.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"MsoNormal\"\u003e\u003cb\u003eIngredients:\u003c\/b\u003e Aqua, Magnesium lauryl sulfate, Cocamidopropyl betaine, Coco-glucoside, Glyceryl oleate, Guar hydroxypropyltrimonium chloride, Glycerin, Aloe barbadensis leaf juice*, Parfum, Sodium benzoate, Potassium sorbate, Sodium chloride, Benzyl alcohol, Myristyl lactate, Prunus amygdalus dulcis oil, Helianthus annuus seed oil, Citric acid, Calendula officinalis extract, Dehydroacetic acid, Mel*, Propolis, Tocopherol.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"MsoNormal\"\u003e*Organic\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"MsoNormal\"\u003eNatural product with physiological pH 4.5-5.5\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"MsoNormal\"\u003eAnimal Friendly | No Paraffin | No Silicones | No Parabens | 100% Recyclable\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"MsoNormal\"\u003e“Less plastic is fantastic” packaging is using 70% less plastic compared to a normal bottle pack. Less bulk, being soft and doesn’t break, generates a better recycling chain and allows use of all its contents.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"MsoNormal\"\u003eBy purchasing BEE IT cosmetics  you contribute to the creation of new bee oasis. \u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"MsoNormal\"\u003eMade in Italy\u003c\/p\u003e","brand":"BEE IT","offers":[{"title":"Default Title","offer_id":52138376954183,"sku":null,"price":5.9,"currency_code":"EUR","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0790\/6829\/9591\/files\/bee-it-shampoo-body-wash-pink-for-kids-250ml-813819.png?v=1739897342"},{"product_id":"bee-it-shampoo-body-wash-blue-for-kids-50ml","title":"BEE IT Shampoo \u0026 Body Wash Blue for Kids 50ml","description":"\u003cp class=\"MsoNormal\"\u003ePhysiological pH shampoo \u0026amp; body wash rich in natural ingredients to enjoy the bath time as a pleasant experience of play and creativity. With organic aloe vera, sweet almond oil, organic honey and propolis, for a delicate and nourishing action.\u003cbr\u003eAmused and clean, his hair will be velvety and luminous, and his skin will be even softer and more fragrant.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"MsoNormal\"\u003e\u003cb\u003eHow to use:\u003c\/b\u003e Apply to hair and body and massage gently, then rinse.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"MsoNormal\"\u003e\u003cb\u003eIngredients:\u003c\/b\u003e Aqua, Magnesium lauryl sulfate, Cocamidopropyl betaine, Coco-glucoside, Glyceryl oleate, Guar hydroxypropyltrimonium chloride, Glycerin, Aloe barbadensis leaf juice*, Parfum, Sodium benzoate, Potassium sorbate, Sodium chloride, Benzyl alcohol, Myristyl lactate, Prunus amygdalus dulcis oil, Helianthus annuus seed oil, Citric acid, Calendula officinalis extract, Dehydroacetic acid, Mel*, Propolis, Tocopherol.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"MsoNormal\"\u003e*Organic\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"MsoNormal\"\u003eNatural product with physiological pH 4.5-5.5\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"MsoNormal\"\u003eAnimal Friendly | No Paraffin | No Silicones | No Parabens | 100% Recyclable\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"MsoNormal\"\u003e“Less plastic is fantastic” packaging is using 70% less plastic compared to a normal bottle pack. Less bulk, being soft and doesn’t break, generates a better recycling chain and allows use of all its contents.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"MsoNormal\"\u003eBy purchasing BEE IT cosmetics  you contribute to the creation of new bee oasis. \u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"MsoNormal\"\u003eMade in Italy\u003c\/p\u003e","brand":"BEE IT","offers":[{"title":"Default Title","offer_id":52138385801543,"sku":null,"price":5.9,"currency_code":"EUR","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0790\/6829\/9591\/files\/bee-it-shampoo-body-wash-blue-for-kids-250ml-687213.png?v=1739897342"},{"product_id":"bee-it-shampoo-body-wash-blue-for-kids-50ml-copy","title":"BEE IT Shampoo \u0026 Body Wash for Kids Maya 250ml","description":"\u003cp class=\"MsoNormal\"\u003ePhysiological pH shampoo and body wash rich in natural ingredients to to enjoy the bath time as a pleasant experience of play and creativity. With organic aloe vera, sweet almond oil, organic honey and propolis, for a delicate and nourishing action.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"MsoNormal\"\u003eAmused and clean, leaves hair velvety and luminous and skin soft.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"MsoNormal\"\u003e\u003cb\u003eHow to use:\u003c\/b\u003e Apply to hair and body and massage gently, then rinse.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"MsoNormal\"\u003e\u003cb\u003eIngredients:\u003c\/b\u003e Aqua, Magnesium lauryl sulfate, Cocamidopropyl betaine, Coco-glucoside, Glyceryl oleate, Guar hydroxypropyltrimonium chloride, Glycerin, Aloe barbadensis leaf juice*, Parfum, Sodium benzoate, Potassiu\u003cimg\u003em sorbate, Sodium chloride, Benzyl alcohol, Myristyl lactate, Prunus amygdalus dulcis oil, Helianthus annuus seed oil, Citric acid, Calendula officinalis extract, Dehydroacetic acid, Mel*, Propolis, Tocopherol.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"MsoNormal\"\u003e*Organic\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"MsoNormal\"\u003eNatural product with physiological pH 4.5-5.5\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"MsoNormal\"\u003eAnimal Friendly | No Paraffin | No Silicones | No Parabens | 100% Recyclable\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"MsoNormal\"\u003e“Less plastic is fantastic” packaging is using 70% less plastic compared to a normal bottle pack. Less bulk, being soft and doesn’t break, generates a better recycling chain and allows use of all its contents.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"MsoNormal\"\u003eBy purchasing BEE IT cosmetics  you contribute to the creation of new bee oasis. \u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"MsoNormal\"\u003eMade in Italy\u003c\/p\u003e","brand":"BEE IT","offers":[{"title":"Default Title","offer_id":52143596339527,"sku":null,"price":12.0,"currency_code":"EUR","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0790\/6829\/9591\/files\/bee-it-shampoo-body-wash-for-kids-maya-250ml-2802370.png?v=1756222789"},{"product_id":"bee-it-shampoo-body-wash-for-kids-maya-50ml","title":"BEE IT Shampoo \u0026 Body Wash for Kids Maya 50ml","description":"\u003cp class=\"MsoNormal\"\u003ePhysiological pH shampoo and body wash rich in natural ingredients to to enjoy the bath time as a pleasant experience of play and creativity. With organic aloe vera, sweet almond oil, organic honey and propolis, for a delicate and nourishing action.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"MsoNormal\"\u003eAmused and clean, leaves hair velvety and luminous and skin soft.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"MsoNormal\"\u003e\u003cb\u003eHow to use:\u003c\/b\u003e Apply to hair and body and massage gently, then rinse.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"MsoNormal\"\u003e\u003cb\u003eIngredients:\u003c\/b\u003e Aqua, Magnesium lauryl sulfate, Cocamidopropyl betaine, Coco-glucoside, Glyceryl oleate, Guar hydroxypropyltrimonium chloride, Glycerin, Aloe barbadensis leaf juice*, Parfum, Sodium benzoate, Potassiu\u003cimg\u003em sorbate, Sodium chloride, Benzyl alcohol, Myristyl lactate, Prunus amygdalus dulcis oil, Helianthus annuus seed oil, Citric acid, Calendula officinalis extract, Dehydroacetic acid, Mel*, Propolis, Tocopherol.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"MsoNormal\"\u003e*Organic\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"MsoNormal\"\u003eNatural product with physiological pH 4.5-5.5\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"MsoNormal\"\u003eAnimal Friendly | No Paraffin | No Silicones | No Parabens | 100% Recyclable\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"MsoNormal\"\u003e“Less plastic is fantastic” packaging is using 70% less plastic compared to a normal bottle pack. Less bulk, being soft and doesn’t break, generates a better recycling chain and allows use of all its contents.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"MsoNormal\"\u003eBy purchasing BEE IT cosmetics  you contribute to the creation of new bee oasis. \u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"MsoNormal\"\u003eMade in Italy\u003c\/p\u003e","brand":"BEE IT","offers":[{"title":"Default Title","offer_id":52143676195143,"sku":null,"price":5.9,"currency_code":"EUR","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0790\/6829\/9591\/files\/bee-it-shampoo-body-wash-for-kids-maya-50ml-4970425.png?v=1756222789"},{"product_id":"bee-it-sun-spf50-maya-50ml","title":"BEE IT SUN SPF50 Maya 50ml","description":"\u003cp class=\"MsoNormal\"\u003eHigh protection sun milk, effective and protecting the skin from both UVA and UVB rays. Suitable for sensitive skin and also suitable for kids under 3 years old. Protects skin against aging, sun spots and keeps skin hydrated.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"MsoNormal\"\u003eAlso effective in protecting the bees!\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"MsoNormal\"\u003e\u003cb\u003eHow to use:\u003c\/b\u003e Apply to face\/body before sun exposure until absorbed. Repeat the application frequently for a safe, even and long-lasting tan.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"MsoNormal\"\u003e\u003cb\u003eIngredients:\u003c\/b\u003e Aqua [Water], Ethylhexyl methoxycinnamate, Octocrylene, Butyl methoxydibenzoylmethane, Methylene bis-benzotriazolyl tetramethylbutylphenol, Helianthus annuus (Sunflower) seed oil, Glyceryl stearate SE, Prunus amygdalus dulcis (Sweet almond) oil, Glycerin, Phenoxyethanol, Decyl glucoside, Tocopheryl acetate, Citric acid, Parfum [Fragrance], Ethylhexylglycerin, Aloe barbadensis leaf juice*, Tetrasodium glutamate diacetate, Olea europaea (Olive) fruit oil*, Oryza sativa (Rice) bran oil, Vitis vinifera (Grape) seed oil, Allantoin, Propylene glycol, Xanthan gum, Vaccinium myrtillus (Myrtle) fruit extract, Avena sativa (Oat) kernel extract*, Calendula officinalis flower extract*, Sodium hydroxide, Mel\/Honey*, Propolis wax, Sodium benzoate, Potassium sorbate.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"MsoNormal\"\u003e*Organic\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"MsoNormal\"\u003eAnimal Friendly | No Paraffin | No Silicones | No Parabens | 100% Recyclable\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"MsoNormal\"\u003e“Less plastic is fantastic” packaging is using 70% less plastic compared to a normal bottle pack. Less bulk, being soft and doesn’t break, generates a better recycling chain and allows use of all its contents.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"MsoNormal\"\u003eBy purchasing BEE IT cosmetics  you contribute to the creation of new bee oasis. \u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"MsoNormal\"\u003eMade in Italy\u003c\/p\u003e","brand":"BEE IT","offers":[{"title":"Default Title","offer_id":52143723315527,"sku":null,"price":9.9,"currency_code":"EUR","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0790\/6829\/9591\/files\/bee-it-sun-spf50-maya-50ml-7388105.png?v=1756222789"}],"url":"https:\/\/bioskina.com\/collections\/lapsed.oembed","provider":"bioskina","version":"1.0","type":"link"}